"AWSTemplateFormatVersion: \"2010-09-09\"\nDescription: >\n  Luciel Step 28 Phase 2 verification gate task role. Provisions\n  luciel-ecs-verify-role for the Pattern N one-shot Fargate task that\n  runs python -m app.verification against the prod ALB\n  (https://api.vantagemind.ai). Least-privilege scoping: read-only on\n  exactly two SSM SecureString parameters\n  (/luciel/production/platform-admin-key and\n  /luciel/production/worker_database_url), KMS Decrypt only via the SSM\n  service principal, and no write/list/describe surface beyond what the\n  harness imports require. CloudWatch Logs writes are handled by the\n  pre-existing luciel-ecs-execution-role (shared with mint and worker\n  TDs).\n\n  Region: ca-central-1\n  Account: 729005488042\n  Reference: docs/runbooks/step-28-phase-2-deploy.md sect 8\n\nResources:\n  LucielEcsVerifyRole:\n    Type: AWS::IAM::Role\n    Properties:\n      RoleName: luciel-ecs-verify-role\n      Description: >\n        Task role for the one-shot Pattern N verification harness. Read\n        scope is exactly two SSM SecureStrings: the platform admin API\n        key (used by HTTP pillars 1-8, 10-19) and the worker DSN (used\n        by pillar 9 schema-introspection subprocess). No write surface.\n        No describe/list surface. KMS Decrypt is constrained to the SSM\n        service principal so the role cannot decrypt arbitrary KMS keys.\n      AssumeRolePolicyDocument:\n        Version: \"2012-10-17\"\n        Statement:\n          - Effect: Allow\n            Principal:\n              Service: ecs-tasks.amazonaws.com\n            Action: sts:AssumeRole\n            Condition:\n              ArnLike:\n                aws:SourceArn: !Sub \"arn:aws:ecs:${AWS::Region}:${AWS::AccountId}:*\"\n              StringEquals:\n                aws:SourceAccount: !Ref AWS::AccountId\n      Tags:\n        - Key: luciel:purpose\n          Value: verification-harness\n        - Key: luciel:scope\n          Value: production\n        - Key: luciel:step\n          Value: step-28-phase-2-commit-8\n\n  LucielEcsVerifyRolePolicy:\n    Type: AWS::IAM::Policy\n    Properties:\n      PolicyName: luciel-ecs-verify-role-permissions\n      Roles:\n        - !Ref LucielEcsVerifyRole\n      PolicyDocument:\n        Version: \"2012-10-17\"\n        Statement:\n          - Sid: ReadPlatformAdminKeyForHttpPillars\n            Effect: Allow\n            Action:\n              - ssm:GetParameter\n            Resource:\n              - !Sub \"arn:aws:ssm:${AWS::Region}:${AWS::AccountId}:parameter/luciel/production/platform-admin-key\"\n          - Sid: ReadWorkerDsnForPillar09Subprocess\n            Effect: Allow\n            Action:\n              - ssm:GetParameter\n            Resource:\n              - !Sub \"arn:aws:ssm:${AWS::Region}:${AWS::AccountId}:parameter/luciel/production/worker_database_url\"\n          - Sid: DecryptSsmSecureStringsViaSsm\n            Effect: Allow\n            Action:\n              - kms:Decrypt\n            Resource: \"*\"\n            Condition:\n              StringEquals:\n                kms:ViaService: !Sub \"ssm.${AWS::Region}.amazonaws.com\"\n\nOutputs:\n  VerifyRoleArn:\n    Description: ARN of the verification harness task role\n    Value: !GetAtt LucielEcsVerifyRole.Arn\n    Export:\n      Name: luciel-ecs-verify-role-arn\n  VerifyRoleName:\n    Description: Name of the verification harness task role\n    Value: !Ref LucielEcsVerifyRole\n"
